hiki: Ana o ka likelihood e hiki mai ana kekahi hanana
wahi h\u0101pana: ʻO ka hoʻonohonoho o nā hopena kūpono a pau o kahi hoʻokolohua likelika
hanana: He pūʻulu o nā hopena i hāʻawi ʻia i kahi kūpono
hopena: He hopena paha o ka hoʻokolohua likelika
awelika: Huina waiwai i puunaueia me ka helu o na waiwai
ho\u02bbokolohua ma\u02bbamau: He kaʻina hana i ʻike ʻole ʻia ka hopena a ʻike ʻia
hiki ole: He hanana me ka hiki ʻole
k\u016b\u02bboko\u02bba: Hoʻoponopono ʻia e a i ʻole e pili ana i nā manawa like no kēlā me kēia mea
la\u02bbana: He hapa o ka heluna kanaka
